        {
            "id": 6415168,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 昶昕(8438)大漲7.02%，報86.9元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昶昕(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:8438:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8438\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8438-TW</a>)10日12:04股價上漲5.7元，報86.9元，漲幅7.02%，成交2,668張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昶昕(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:8438:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8438\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8438-TW</a>)所屬產業為綠能環保，主要業務為資源回收再生產品研發產製與銷售。特用化學品研發產製與銷售。其他綠色產品與設備之研發與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲14.04%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲7.03%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,801 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,716 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-6 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+91 張</li> <li>融資增減：+533 張</li> <li>融券增減：+67 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6415168",
